  m_Name: Bunny
  m_EditorClassIdentifier: Assembly-CSharp::DocumentItem
  documentTitle: Bunny
  documentText: "I won Bunbun at the spelling bee for getting first place, and Papa
    was really happy for me. He even tried to fix the dryer so Bunbun could smell
    like the flowery detergent he picked out. But it didn\u2019t spin right and made
    a loud noise before stopping. Now she\u2019s not as soft anymore. Mama got upset
    and said he always makes things worse"
